
Overview of verb advise

The verb advise has 3 senses (first 3 from tagged texts)
                                         
1. (11) rede, advise, counsel -- (give advice to; "The teacher counsels troubled students"; "The lawyer counselled me when I was accused of tax fraud")
2. (10) advise, notify, give notice, send word, apprise, apprize -- (inform (somebody) of something; "I advised him that the rent was due")
3. (4) propose, suggest, advise -- (make a proposal, declare a plan for something; "the senator proposed to abolish the sales tax")
